									<li>HTML Tags</li>
									<ul>
										<li>&lt;h1&gt; to &lt;h6&gt;: Headings of different sizes.</li>
										<li>&lt;p&gt;: Paragraph tag for textual content.</li>
										<li>&lt;a href="#"&gt;: Anchor tag to create links.</li>
										<li>&lt;img src="image.jpg" alt="Description"&gt;: Image tag to display images.</li>
									</ul>

									<li>Lists</li>
