										<li><code>&lt;input type="checkbox"&gt;</code>: Checkbox for multiple selections.</li>
										<li><code>&lt;select&gt;</code>: Dropdown menu for selecting options.</li>
										<li><code>&lt;textarea&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;</code>: Area for multi-line text input.</li>
									</ul>

									<li>Tables</li>
									<ul>
